      • build

        public static CRUDApplicationProfile build​(URL url,
                                           DataFactory dataFactory,
                                           org.apache.jena.rdf.model.Resource resource)
                                    throws SaiException
        Builder used by a DataFactory to construct and initialize a CRUDApplicationProfile. If a Jena resource is provided and there is already a CRUDApplicationProfile at the provided url, the graph of the provided resource will be used. The remote graph will not be updated until CRUDResource.update() is called.
        Parameters:
        url - URL of the CRUDApplicationProfile to build
        dataFactory - DataFactory to assign
        resource - Optional Jena Resource to populate the resource graph
        Returns:
        CRUDApplicationProfile
        Throws:
        SaiException
